# Editor / OS noise
# =============================================================================

.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
*.bak
*.tmp
~$*.docx
~WRL*.tmp

# =============================================================================
# Allow-list overrides — files we WANT to keep despite patterns above
# =============================================================================

# Keep per-subdir READMEs even when the subdir is largely gitignored
!**/README.md

# Chat handoff documents — local-only context-preservation artifacts;
# NOT part of the scientific project. Both session-1 and session-2 handoffs
# now live in the sibling _chat_artifacts/ directory (outside this repo
# entirely; per session-1 Part 14 §C2 recommendation; consistent naming
# convention `CHAT_HANDOFF_<DATE>_session<N>.md`). Since they live outside
# the repo tree, no .gitignore rule needed; this comment is kept as a
# pointer for anyone wondering where the chat handoffs went.
# - 2026-05-08 session 1: ../_chat_artifacts/CHAT_HANDOFF_2026-05-08_session1.md (was: CHAT HANDOFF LandSyMM-IMOGEN.md, moved 2026-05-09)
# - 2026-05-08 session 2: ../_chat_artifacts/CHAT_HANDOFF_2026-05-08_session2.md
